{"tid":2350400,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你吞永痕, 駛撚安心出行咩","createTime":"2021-01-02T09:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T09:35:49.000Z","uid":269706,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef12f1e05422d956256945c1c9e59e9461781b6","tid":2350400,"uid":269706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"根本就好撚簡單<br />\n<br />\n依家大部份既social media apps, android, ios, 都會收集你電話既GPS,<br />\n只要每個人同意番個D APP 或者 OS收GPS.<br />\n<br />\n到有L樣確診, 就確診者自己send自己既ID去big data collector.話賴左野, (或者閪政府send個確診者email去big data collector)<br />\n然後big data collector 就可以計番<br />\n其他人喺咩時間咩地方出現過既感染機會, 仲可以用APP send番個通知msg....<br />\n<br />\n閪政府仲可以驗屎渠, 有毒既location又send 去google...<br />\n<br />\n基本上只要你去過兩個location痾屎, 而兩個location都查到有毒, 已經可以確定你有感染機會...<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知點樣可以將呢個方法腥俾facebook google叫佢做, 而佢會至少睇到?"},{"pid":"f6b434dad0ad629538a56a57fd8302517ee91d58","tid":2350400,"uid":51754,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:24:59.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">[求推] 衞生署 強制檢測名單 又双叒叕有錯？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a></span>"},{"pid":"459df6ca988d8d3db0eaf20ac9325e8ddb263e46","tid":2350400,"uid":282757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:34:06.000Z","msg":"睇到都唔做啦，Apple Google研發個個API咪一樣唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5006194f9bb3be8a6c0075e24469442f3e95c93e","tid":2350400,"uid":269706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"已經send左GOOGLE"},{"pid":"cb1fe7103bea4215a9616639e986f0643ba82c8c","tid":2350400,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"佢壇dbiz 做到佢癲左"}]}